IMEYA kaMasipala weTheku, uNkk Zandile Gumede, iyazichitha njengamampunge izinsolo ezithi impilo yayo isengcupheni.&nbsp; UNkk Gumede uthe ngeke aze amoshe isikhathi sakhe akhulume ngalolu daba ngoba lungamampunge. UNkk Gumede uphawule kanje izolo ngemuva kokuvela kwemibiko kwabezindaba ethi impilo yakhe ayiphephile.</p> Lolu daba luqale ukuvela ngempelasonto, ngesinye sezikhulu zamaphoyisa omkhandlu uSuperintendent Sibonelo Mchunu okubikwe ukuthi ubhalele i-email iPhini leMeya uNkk Fawzia Peer embikela ngokuthi impilo yemeya ayiphephile. </p> Kule email uMchunu usole umphathi wamaphoyisa omkhandlu uMnuz Eugene Nzama ngokuthi udala ukuthi imeya ingaphephi ngenxa yokugxambukela kwakhe okunenhlese yepolitiki.</p> UMchunu uthe njalo uNkk Gumede uma enza umsebenzi womkhandlu usuke engaphephile ngokwanele.</p> Uthe wumbango wepolitiki owenza ukuthi uNkk Gumede angaphephi.</p> UMchunu uthe usaba ukuthi uNkk Gumede angase asocongwe kulandela ukuxegiswa kwezokuphepha zakhe ngamabomu.</p> Uthe uNzama kade aqala ukugxambukela kwezokuphepha zikaNkk Gumede.</p> UMchunu naye uthe kade ayekhala kubaphathi bomkhandlu ngokuthi naye uzibona engaphephile.</p> Uthe ukukhala ngezokuphepha kukaNkk Gumede ukususela ekubulaweni kwamanye amakhansela, okubalwa kuwo uMnuz Wiseman Mshibe, Mnuz Sbu Shezi noMnuz Sbu Sibiya owayenguNobhala we-ANC eThekwini.</p> UNkk Gumede uphawule kanje izolo ngemuva kokuvela kwemibiko kwabezindaba ethi impilo yakhe ayiphephile.Lolu daba luqale ukuvela ngempelasonto, ngesinye sezikhulu zamaphoyisa omkhandlu uSuperintendent Sibonelo Mchunu okubikwe ukuthi ubhalele i-email iPhini leMeya uNkk Fawzia Peer embikela ngokuthi impilo yemeya ayiphephile. Kule email uMchunu usole umphathi wamaphoyisa omkhandlu uMnuz Eugene Nzama ngokuthi udala ukuthi imeya ingaphephi ngenxa yokugxambukela kwakhe okunenhlese yepolitiki.UMchunu uthe njalo uNkk Gumede uma enza umsebenzi womkhandlu usuke engaphephile ngokwanele.Uthe wumbango wepolitiki owenza ukuthi uNkk Gumede angaphephi.UMchunu uthe usaba ukuthi uNkk Gumede angase asocongwe kulandela ukuxegiswa kwezokuphepha zakhe ngamabomu.Uthe uNzama kade aqala ukugxambukela kwezokuphepha zikaNkk Gumede.UMchunu naye uthe kade ayekhala kubaphathi bomkhandlu ngokuthi naye uzibona engaphephile.Uthe ukukhala ngezokuphepha kukaNkk Gumede ukususela ekubulaweni kwamanye amakhansela, okubalwa kuwo uMnuz Wiseman Mshibe, Mnuz Sbu Shezi noMnuz Sbu Sibiya owayenguNobhala we-ANC eThekwini.